diatric Intensive and Critical Care Societies. These guidelines were solely funded by the European Society of Intensive Care Medicine and the Society of Critical Care Medicine.</p></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby="author-information" data-title="Author information"><div class="c-article-section" id="author-information-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="author-information">Author information</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="author-information-content"><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="affiliations">Authors and Affiliations</h3><ol class="c-article-author-affiliation__list"><li id="Aff1"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Children’s Hospital of Philadelphia, University of Pennsylvania Perelman School of Medicine, Philadelphia, PA, USA</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Scott L. Weiss, Akira Nishisaki &amp; Judy T. Verger</p></li><li id="Aff2"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Great Ormond Street Hospital for Children, London, UK</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Mark J. Peters &amp; Joe Brierley</p></li><li id="Aff3"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Medicine, Division of Critical Care, McMaster University, Hamilton, ON, Canada</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Waleed Alhazzani &amp; Karen Choong</p></li><li id="Aff4"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Health Research Methods and Impact, McMaster University, Hamilton, ON, Canada</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Waleed Alhazzani &amp; Karen Choong</p></li><li id="Aff5"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Pediatrics, Boston Children’s Hospital and Harvard Medical School, Boston, MA, USA</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Michael S. D. Agus &amp; Robert C. Tasker</p></li><li id="Aff6"><p class="c-