-track-label="link">Septic shock</a></span></li><li class="c-article-subject-list__subject"><span><a href="/search?query=Surviving%20Sepsis%20Campaign&amp;facet-discipline=&#34;Medicine%20%26%20Public%20Health&#34;" data-track="click" data-track-action="view keyword" data-track-label="link">Surviving Sepsis Campaign</a></span></li></ul><div data-component="article-info-list"></div></div></div></div></div></section>

                    
